OL,3,CNo fireworks and stage show for
OL,4,CLeicester's Diwali celebrations
OL,6,FLeicester's Diwali celebrations - said
OL,7,Fto be the biggest outside of India -
OL,8,Fwill be scaled down this year.
OL,10,FThere will be no fireworks and
OL,11,Ftraditional stage show during the
OL,12,FBelgrave Road celebrations on October
OL,13,F20, the city council said.
OL,15,FThe Diwali Village, with food stalls
OL,16,Fand funfair rides, will also not go
OL,17,Fahead.
