OL,3,CNo fireworks and stage show for
OL,4,CLeicester's Diwali celebrations
OL,6,FIt is after concerns were raised by
OL,7,Fthe city's Safety Advisory Group,
OL,8,Fafter the event attracted around
OL,9,F50,000 people last year.
OL,11,FThe group, which includes
OL,12,Frepresentatives from the city council,
OL,13,Fpolice and other emergency services,
OL,14,Frejected plans for the "additional
OL,15,Factivities".
OL,17,FBut the council said there will be the
OL,18,FDiwali lights and the Wheel of Light.
