OL,3,CNo fireworks and stage show for
OL,4,CLeicester's Diwali celebrations
OL,6,FLeicester City Mayor Sir Peter Soulsby
OL,7,Fsaid: "I completely understand and
OL,8,Fshare the great desire to make
OL,9,FLeicester's Diwali celebrations as
OL,10,Fgood as can be. I thought that some of
OL,11,Fthe suggestions put forward by the
OL,12,Flocal community were achievable, but
OL,13,Fthe safety advisory group has rejected
OL,14,Fthem all.
OL,16,F"I'm disappointed that as a result
OL,17,Fthere won't be any additional
OL,18,Factivities, and I hope this is
OL,19,Fsomething the SAG will review next
OL,20,Fyear."
